# Prototype code (studio)

Prototypes validate ideas; production polish lives in `src/**`.

## Allowed

- Hardcoded values, minimal comments, simple architecture, globals, copy-paste, debug prints, placeholders.

## Required

- Each prototype in `prototypes/[name]/` with a `README.md` documenting hypothesis, how to run, and outcome.
- Do not import prototype code from `src/**` — keep boundaries clear.
